(29649, 'Westair 4 mg 14 sachets', 'ويست اير 4مجم 14 كيس', '70', '98', 'Montelukast', 'Western pharmaceuticals industries', 'Sachet', 'أكياس', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '4 mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
